Story_Texts.SourceString: You see an idyllic castle ahead.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: You see an idyllic castle ahead.

Story_Texts.SourceString: As you approach, it slowly twists and fades.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: As you approach, it slowly twists and fades.

Story_Texts.SourceString: The false castle falls away before your eyes.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: The false castle falls away before your eyes.

Story_Texts.SourceString: What sort of evil could cause these delusions?
